  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So soccer game, that is one of the hobby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And basketball, that was the other hobby, and tennis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, in Romania were the Carpathian mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were climbing the mountain, because we owned some of the forest, the Bronsteins, what we cut for the sawmill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went on top 3,000-foot high mountains, maybe higher, stay, and then we came down the mountains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a flock, pardon me-- a float, you know, what from the wood, like they make it in Canada, put together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were going down about 10 miles on a beautiful river with all the cousins and arrive around the sawmill, where they pulled on out the wood for the sawmill.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was-- summer is unbelievable, right on the mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, reports didn't have to come from Germany, because it was Romania, actually, they changed on later on to the Iron Guard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are talking in '36, '37, something in that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the, actually, a revolution with tanks and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- especially major cities like Bucharest, or so really rollin' on the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the main newspaper, which was called [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], that was like an official organ the Romanian Iron Guard-- published on the front line a big picture, black and white-- I remember like today-- big, as big as newspapers can be.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it says-- and they show a slaughterhouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm talking about that because you ask reports.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't necessary report because you actually had it home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't need-- you knew what's going on in Germany, but that's beside the point.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
